  "texts": [
    "By enabling any changes to be detected, this prevents alteration of the EMRs kept encrypted on the document-oriented database.",
    "A descriptive summary is also included in the blockchain that gives an overview of each patient's disease and EMR.",
    "The descriptive summaries are unencrypted and contain keywords about the patients.",
    "Using the descriptive summary, third-party entities can gain insight about a patient without accessing the patient's sensitive EMR.",
    "The descriptive summaries are of great importance when requesting patients for permission to access their EMRs."
  ],
